---
title: Thyme and Honey Pork Chops over Couscous with a Apple Arugula Salad
description: How do you shake up dinnertime? Grab an apple! The fall fruit brings an unexpected but utterly delicious twist to the green salad in this recipe. That sweetness also gets echoed in the honey herb sauce that’s drizzled over the centerpiece: juicy, pan-seared pork chops. It’s all served next to a bed of couscous, which makes this dish feel hearty and satisfying without being overly heavy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thyme-and-honey-pork-chops-b4ac26d3.jpg
